com.paypal.selion.platform.web

Class Page

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.platform.web.Page

  • public final class Page
extends Object
    This class represents the PageYaml V2 file.

    Example file: 
     baseClass: "com.paypal.selion.testcomponents.BasicPageImpl"
 pageTitle:
   US: "API Page"
 elements:
   submitButton:
     US: "//div[@id='apiOption1']/p[3]/a"
 pageValidators: [submitButton]
 defaultLocale: US
